1.0 About
Ropeclient is a text based virtual tabletop for roleplaying online. The 
appearance of the environemnt resembles closely that of MUDs while 
trying to offer a flexible environment to play games in. Game worlds, 
known as universes, can span from single storytelling rooms to detailed 
worlds where the player characters can explore freely.


